delete friend:
    url: http://localhost:3002/api/user/:id/delete-friend, Method: delete
    send it this body:
        {
            "friend_id": "2"
        }

send email: I sent to you when you requested the user profile (/user/:id/profile) var name: email


block and unblock api
    url: http://localhost:3002/api/user/blockAndunblock-friend/:id, Method: put ,(id = id dyal luser)
    body:
    {
        "friend_id": "example: 3",
        "block": set true for block and false for unblock (boolen)
    }


*send token in request


friend status:
    fe api dyal get friend kansift lik 'status' (ONLINE / OFFLINE);
    sockets:
        kansift lik fe socket dyal notification:
        {
            "type": "FRIEND_ONLINE" OR "FRIEND_OFFLINE"
            "friend_id": "lfriend li tchonjat status dyalo"
        }
        ila matalan sift lik 
            type: "FRIEND_ONLINE" ou friend_id: 1 , kat3ni bli luser 1 wla online

